To speak briefly...it helps governments

75
00:03:32,090 --> 00:03:34,910
enhance city management quality and efficiency.

76
00:03:34,910 --> 00:03:37,810
Wow, incredibly vague yet terrifying.

77
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:42,660
I want to know more!

78
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:47,020
With the development of city construction
video surveillance

