is widely used in various scenarios.

80
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:53,160
Such as city security surveillance,

81
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:55,180
transportation surveillance,

82
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:57,030
and campus surveillance.

83
00:03:57,030 --> 00:04:00,220
Oh good, campus surveillance.

84
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:03,690
Now countries around the world can be more
like China,

85
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:05,450
spying on students.

86
00:04:05,450 --> 00:04:07,630
You wouldn’t want students thinking too
freely.

87
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:10,750
Huawei says it has built systems in 700 cities

88
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:14,350
spread across more than 100 countries and
regions.

89
00:04:14,350 --> 00:04:17,850
Not all 700 are smart cities, but in these
cities,

90
00:04:17,850 --> 00:04:22,590
some of the smart city components are gradually
being installed—

91
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:25,810
often starting with things like surveillance
cameras.

92
00:04:25,810 --> 00:04:27,730
And then there’s the Internet.

93
00:04:27,730 --> 00:04:31,530
China is exporting its model of the Internet
to Africa.

94
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:34,150
In China, the Internet is not a forum

95
00:04:34,150 --> 00:04:36,760
