96
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:40,660
It’s a way for the government to monitor
and control people.

97
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:42,150
And the Chinese Communist Party

98
00:04:42,150 --> 00:04:45,400
wants to export its authoritarian model of
the internet

99
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:47,480
around the world.

100
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,650
Africa is a prime testing ground.

101
00:04:49,650 --> 00:04:50,650
Why?

102
00:04:50,650 --> 00:04:53,450
Because most African countries are poor,

103
00:04:53,450 --> 00:04:55,070
meaning they don’t have a lot of

104
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:58,060
