And things got worse.

128
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,320
As the Wall Street Journal says,

129
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:08,270
“A few years ago, the East and Southern
African nations

130
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:11,560
